<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Marriage Dashboard</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    body {
      margin:0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f1f2e, #2b2b45);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      max-width: 400px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }

    .progress {
      background: #444;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .progress-bar {
      width: 100%;
      background: #ff6b81;
      padding: 5px;
    }

    button {
      background: #ff6b81;
      border: none;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      color: white;
      font-size: 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 15px;
      transition: 0.2s;
    }

    button:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    a.invite {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      background: #4dabf7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .heart {
      font-size: 30px;
      animation: float 1s ease infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      from {transform: translateY(0);}
      to {transform: translateY(-10px);}
    }

  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>💍 Marriage Dashboard</h1>
    <p>데이터 기반 의사결정 결과, 인생 장기 프로젝트를 시작합니다.</p>

    <div class="card">
      <p>상태값: SINGLE → MARRIED</p>
      <p>처리일시: 2026.XX.XX</p>
      <p>담당자: ○○○ & ○○○</p>

      <div class="progress">
        <div class="progress-bar">100%</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>💖 축하 이벤트</h3>
      <button onclick="like()">👍 축하해주기</button>
      <p>현재 축하 수: <span id="count">0</span></p>
      <div id="hearts"></div>
    </div>

    <a href="여기에_청첩장_URL" target="_blank" class="invite">
      📩 모바일 청첩장 보러가기
    </a>
  </div>

<script>
  let count = 0;

  function like() {
    count++;
    document.getElementById("count").innerText = count;

    const heart = document.createElement("div");
    heart.innerHTML = "💖";
    heart.className = "heart";

    document.getElementById("hearts").appendChild(heart);

    setTimeout(() => {
      heart.remove();
    }, 1000);
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
